array
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% ARRAY — syntax quick-ref
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% Header/items:
%%   array                         (block form; directives below)
%%   cells <v1> <v2> …             (items in block form)
%%   array <v1> <v2> …             (inline form)
%%   title <text>
%% Gap:
%%   literal ... in cells = one elided-middle cell rendered as …
%%   At most one; it must be between concrete cells, not first or last.
%% Axis:    axis horizontal (default) · axis vertical
%% Index:   index · index bottom · index reverse · index bottom reverse
%%          bottom uses the opposite side; reverse numbers n-1 → 0.
%% Pointers:
%%   ptr <name> -> <target> ["quoted label"]
%%   <target> = logical index value (not physical slot; reverse/gap-aware), cN, cfirst, clast, cgap.
%% Anchors: c0 … cN (logical cells; gap has no cN) · cfirst · clast · cgap
%% Poster links:
%%   arrayName.cN · arrayName.cfirst · arrayName.clast · arrayName.cgap
%%   arrayName[i] · arrayName[-1]  (negative counts from end; -1 = clast)
%% Comments: full-line %% text is stripped before parse; inline/trailing %% is not.
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  title Sample array
  cells 5 8 13 21 34
  index bottom
  ptr p -> 2
  ptr q -> 4
